<sn><md>### Basic Concept of Respiration

* Respiration releases the stored energy of food molecules.
* It involves oxidation of glucose.
* The final product is ATP, which drives all cellular work.
* Carbon dioxide and water are formed as end products in aerobic respiration.
</md></sn><sn><md>### Respiration With and Without Oxygen

